## 专题对比文档
在 `content/topics/<topic-slug>.md` 下创建，front matter 包含：
```yaml
---
title: "专题标题"
games: ["game1", "game2"]  # 涉及的游戏
tags: []
date: <today>
status: "draft"
---
```